[[/div]]

[[div class="raisa_memo" style="text-align: left"]]

After the twentieth identical request to add to the description of the following SCP, we have elected to place the new content (as supplied so generously by Esoteric Logics & Ritualistics) as the fourth addendum to this document, __not__ in the description. This decision is final. As made clear multiple times, the proposed additions are highly speculative, rely on non-standard frameworks, and are non-compliant to extant guidelines for descriptions. As a primarily physical object, SCP-9338 does not meet the necessary criteria to permit an irregular description. Any attempts to challenge this decision would be most decidedly //illogical//.

[[div style="text-align: right; font-size: 0.9em; font-style: italic"]]
19/01/21
Sarah Emma Ames
Senior Administrator (Site-512), RAISA
[[/div]]

[[/div]]


