Tabitha, to what do I owe the pleasure? Yes, I know you know I knew.

I'm perfectly happy to pass the skip to you. (I won't insult you by claiming it goes to your department; I know you are more than capable, and likely willing, to monopolise the research on this one.) I think Dr. Qiu also has an inkling of what this skip really is, and I would bet that he wants EL&R to get it as badly as you do. It really was a pleasure collaborating with you last time, and I always look forward to what you produce.

But I stole the skip for a reason. I know there are some projects you're working on right now, some of which are quite unfairly restricted to EL&R. I know most of them are restricted for good reasons. But I've heard chatter about a certain Project Circe.

I think we can work out a deal. Game?
-----
SCP or whatever it stands for,

Dr. Wayland Laurence Pan
Head Researcher
Experimentation & Paratechnology
Site-512
